There are large car parks for patients and visitors, for which charges apply. To view charges, please vlew our website. Some visitors are exempt from payment: eg: parents staying overnight with very sick children; patients undergoing treatment such as radiotherapy; parents feeding babies on the Neo Natal Unit. 
